{"id": "art-20299", "label": "Art. 20299", "title": "Art. 20299: Încetarea mandatului de ocrotire", "slug": "art-20299", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1444200401\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1062\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1444200401\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 2029<sup>9</sup>:\nÎncetarea mandatului de ocrotire </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_56379863\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1061\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_56379863\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259; au încetat cauzele care au provocat\nîncuviin&#355;area mandatului, mandatarul este obligat s&#259; sesizeze de\nîndat&#259; instan&#355;a de tutel&#259; în vederea constat&#259;rii\nîncet&#259;rii execut&#259;rii contractului ca urmare a redobândirii de\nc&#259;tre mandant a capacit&#259;&#355;ii de exerci&#355;iu. Dac&#259;\nmandantul este îngrijit într-o institu&#355;ie sanitar&#259;, aceea&#351;i\nobliga&#355;ie revine &#351;i acestei institu&#355;ii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1544968583\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1060\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1544968583\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Mandatul înceteaz&#259; s&#259; produc&#259; efecte\ndac&#259; instan&#355;a constat&#259; încetarea execut&#259;rii contractului ca\nurmare a redobândirii de c&#259;tre mandant a capacit&#259;&#355;ii de\nexerci&#355;iu.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1854496974\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1059\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1854496974\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Mandantul redevenit capabil poate revoca oricând\nmandatul.</span></p>"}